<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880726-0165 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News: Gleason Corp. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> WNEWS GLE </CO><DATELINE> GLEASON Corp. (Rochester, N.Y.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Richard J. Bonnie, formerly executive vice president of the Gleason Works division, was named its president. He succeeds Albert W. Moore, who continues as corporate executive vice president-operations and a director. Gleason Corp. makes gear-production equipment and other industrial products. </TEXT></DOC>